name: mecha_musume
description:
This is a 2D style version of mecha Lora. At the same time, it strengthens the expression of details. Basic model remains unchanged, prompt words refer to upload sample. Of course you can be bold and offer different ideas.

base model is sunshinemix. On the sunshinemix model will work best.(old version)

base model is watch__00500_V1(watch_movie), On the sunshinemix model will work best.

Usage

These are my settings I always use it is recommended but not essential;

Steps: 20+

Sampler: Euler

CFG scale: 7 to 10

weight: <=0.5
